1
00:00:48,890 --> 00:00:52,990
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,460 --> 00:00:56,060
[Episode 23]

3
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,410
How did it go?

4
00:01:23,810 --> 00:01:25,539
Did you find any other deities?

5
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,740
What's happening?

6
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:35,990
Doctor. Doctor!

7
00:01:35,990 --> 00:01:36,780
No! No.

8
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,800
That's not it.

9
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,960
There's a disturbance in the energy field.

10
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,150
This isn't something

11
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:08,080
from our world.

12
00:02:08,650 --> 00:02:09,710
It's a cyber bird.

13
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,120
It's crying.

14
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,770
It's crying tears of blood.

15
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,590
It must be trying to tell us

16
00:02:17,590 --> 00:02:18,990
something important.

17
00:02:19,590 --> 00:02:20,800
Maybe it's about Ya.

18
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:25,240
But we can't communicate with it at all.

19
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:26,960
Go get Xu

20
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,020
and his wife.

21
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:29,190
Do we need to create

22
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:30,590
a temporary dimensional space?

23
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:31,050
No need.

24
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:32,750
Extract its data,

25
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:33,800
and I'll create a projection

26
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,590
right here in the room.

27
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:34,960
Okay.

28
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,040
Analyze the code now.

29
00:02:41,090 --> 00:02:41,490
Done.

30
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,560
Yan Yuzhen

31
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,680
killed my beloved.

32
00:03:07,130 --> 00:03:08,670
Push hard! Don't give up!

33
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,730
It's almost out!

34
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:16,960
Ya!

35
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,030
Ya!

36
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,560
Look, it's the crimson moon!

37
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:24,000
When the crimson moon rises to
the peak of all mountains,

38
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,060
the child of the divine shall be born!

39
00:03:27,590 --> 00:03:28,390
Blood moon...

40
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:31,360
What?

41
00:03:33,050 --> 00:03:34,380
Ya ended up in this state

42
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,260
because Yan Yuzhen poisoned her?

43
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,190
That's too vicious!

44
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,760
Why would she do that?

45
00:03:41,010 --> 00:03:43,070
Because of your unborn child with Ya.

46
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:46,310
She wants to merge

47
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:47,750
the cyber world

48
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,280
and the real world

49
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,400
into a new world.

50
00:03:51,910 --> 00:03:53,030
You once told me

51
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:55,400
Yan Yuzhen was just a wisp of

52
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,590
resentment that resided within a painting

53
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:58,650
and became a demon.

54
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,430
That's what Zhao Li said.

55
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,710
Such a demon should be very weak.

56
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:07,400
How did she become so powerful?

57
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:10,080
She's been working with
Situ Fei all along.

58
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,680
Could Situ Fei be helping her?

59
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,410
Impossible.

60
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,160
Situ Fei

61
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,000
doesn't have that much power.

62
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,390
Yes.

63
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:18,920
People within our company also know

64
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,560
that Situ Fei has always

65
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,430
had a collaborator

66
00:04:20,430 --> 00:04:21,750
who is a very powerful female demon.

67
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:22,510
Her status is

68
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:23,560
higher than Situ Fei's.

69
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:23,960
Right.

70
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,870
She isn't even

71
00:04:25,870 --> 00:04:27,130
a natural-born demon.

72
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,720
Then where does her power come from?

73
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,870
Are you talking about

74
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:32,040
the legendary

75
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,700
peerless beauty, Yan Yuzhen?

76
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:35,530
She has become a demon?

77
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:39,510
What?

78
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,310
I got it.

79
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:43,600
It's thought-based power.

80
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:45,150
The name "Yan Yuzhen"

81
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,000
has circulated through time,

82
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,460
recorded in history books

83
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:50,230
and unofficial chronicles,

84
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,409
and adapted into films, TV series,

85
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:54,100
novels, fan works,

86
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,390
and countless games.

87
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:57,240
Her story, spread in various forms,

88
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,830
means she is constantly mentioned.

89
00:04:58,830 --> 00:05:00,430
Every time she is mentioned,

90
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,490
her power grows a little more.

91
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,310
But

92
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:05,630
from our perspective as demons,

93
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,320
that alone isn't enough.

94
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,150
Being mentioned

95
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,160
can only sustain her existence.

96
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:13,760
She still needs a source
for her demonic power.

97
00:05:14,710 --> 00:05:15,870
Use Love Potion

98
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:18,330
and become more beautiful alongside me.

99
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:21,630
It's the Love Potion.

100
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:22,650
What is that?

101
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:23,750
It's the only product

102
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:24,800
Yan Yuzhen promoted

103
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,120
after becoming a top influencer.

104
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,360
Ya did a lot of work

105
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,560
helping her market it.

106
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:30,870
Every game character like me

107
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:32,530
who has entered the real world

108
00:05:32,570 --> 00:05:33,240
has

109
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,300
monthly KPIs—

110
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:36,190
attract as many fans as possible

111
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:37,720
and give Love Potion to them

112
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,159
as gifts.

113
00:05:39,870 --> 00:05:41,070
The more we give away,

114
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,800
the longer we can stay

115
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,200
in the real world.

116
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:45,080
So,

117
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,950
the very purpose of your existence

118
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:48,480
is to give the Love Potion

119
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,460
to as many humans as possible?

120
00:05:52,270 --> 00:05:53,200
How is that used?

121
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,510
It's a bath product.

122
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,400
You pour it into the bathtub.

123
00:05:57,130 --> 00:05:57,690
So that is

124
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,750
the source of Yan Yuzhen's demonic power.

125
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:01,600
Her fans get the Love Potion,

126
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,140
and while soaking in the bath,

127
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:06,000
they unknowingly transfer energy to her.

128
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,330
It's a very stealthy way

129
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:09,120
to steal human energy

130
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,760
and turn it into her demonic power.

131
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,600
The longer they soak,

132
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,600
the more energy she absorbs.

133
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,330
With so many people bathing...

134
00:06:18,830 --> 00:06:19,750
the demonic power she accumulates

135
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:21,280
becomes truly terrifying.

136
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,460
His code is breaking down.

137
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:32,880
After Yan Yuzhen turned me into a bird,

138
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:35,170
both Wang Fang's code and mine

139
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:36,870
were prohibited from

140
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:38,390
appearing in the real world.

141
00:06:38,390 --> 00:06:40,450
Doing so causes our code to collapse.

142
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,120
Has a virus been injected into the code?

143
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:42,430
Yes.

144
00:06:42,450 --> 00:06:43,360
I can fix it,

145
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,680
but it will take time.

146
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:46,600
I don't think we have that kind of time.

147
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,270
It's okay.

148
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:50,070
My mission is already complete.

149
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,190
I was never

150
00:06:52,190 --> 00:06:53,720
a real living being anyway.

151
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,880
Without Wang Fang...

152
00:06:57,630 --> 00:06:58,600
I have no desire

153
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,860
to continue existing.

154
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:01,310
If we both become mere specks

155
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,510
in the vast universe,

156
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:06,670
that's another way of
being together forever.

157
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:08,610
He's crashing.

158
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:18,320
I hope you can save your wife
and bring her back.

159
00:07:18,610 --> 00:07:19,670
If possible,

160
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,270
please avenge my beloved.

161
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:33,330
He will be a hero to all of humanity,

162
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:35,550
even if

163
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:38,010
he's only a game character.

164
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:39,960
Zhao Hengzhi,

165
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:42,400
let's go find Yan Yuzhen now

166
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:44,350
and stop her evil ambitions.

167
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,210
The fake Kunlun that Yan Yuzhen built

168
00:07:46,210 --> 00:07:47,090
is a model

169
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,520
Situ Fei helped develop.

170
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,060
My wife can get you inside.

171
00:07:50,190 --> 00:07:51,240
So the same logic

172
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,890
applies inside this model?

173
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:53,870
In theory, yes.

174
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,159
But it's hard to say for sure.

175
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:56,390
Last time, we used weapons

176
00:07:56,390 --> 00:07:57,600
conjured through thought-based power.

177
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,400
Xu's computer

178
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,000
has your log from last time.

179
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,000
I'm rewriting the costume program now

180
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,190
and overlaying it with your code.

181
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:05,160
Then you can go straight in
with your equipment.

182
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:05,680
Great.

183
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,660
We'll crush her

184
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,920
and send her running.

185
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,830
But what about the poison in Ya?

186
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,360
She's in this state.

187
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:16,480
Yan Yuzhen is the one

188
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,920
who poisoned Ya.

189
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:19,310
In that case,

190
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,800
as long as we destroy
Yan Yuzhen's demon core

191
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,720
and kill her,

192
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:25,570
the demonic power in reality
will disappear,

193
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,760
and Ya will return to normal.

194
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:29,600
Done.

195
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,170
Extract their codes

196
00:08:31,190 --> 00:08:33,320
and send them into the model directly.

197
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:38,320
Honey,

198
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,890
I will definitely bring you

199
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,010
and our child

200
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:44,030
back safely.

201
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:47,840
You two,

202
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,790
get ready.

203
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,180
What are you doing?

204
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:14,150
The moon has reached its zenith,
and the auspicious moment has arrived.

205
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,550
I must ensure your child

206
00:09:15,550 --> 00:09:16,950
is born safely.

207
00:09:18,670 --> 00:09:20,930
I'm going to perform a cesarean section.

208
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:22,150
No.

209
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:23,150
No!

210
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:24,670
No!

211
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:31,400
Who's there?

212
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:32,390
Dongqing!

213
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:34,000
Dongqing!

214
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:34,430
Honey,

215
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,260
we're here to save you!

216
00:09:36,870 --> 00:09:37,360
Don't believe

217
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,320
that demon's nonsense!

218
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,380
She's up to no good!

219
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,440
Ya!

220
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:50,750
Your wife

221
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:52,150
and the child in her belly

222
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:53,320
are mine.

223
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:55,670
You...

224
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:56,750
Where did you take

225
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:57,720
my wife?

226
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,550
She's just using a trick
to fool your eyes.

227
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:00,550
Ya is still there.

228
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:03,200
She's folded the space around her.

229
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,870
Defeat me,

230
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:16,390
and then you can

231
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:17,270
go home

232
00:10:17,390 --> 00:10:18,870
with your wife and child.

233
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:21,680
But what do you think

234
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:24,120
your odds are of defeating me

235
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,320
in my world?

236
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,700
Dressed up so grandly—

237
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:21,820
what, are you auditioning
for an idol competition?

238
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,150
"Song of Rainbow Skirts and Feather Robes"

239
00:12:02,150 --> 00:12:03,750
is Yan Yuzhen's first skill.

240
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:08,000
It deals 200 damage

241
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,860
with a slowing effect.

242
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:11,640
Let's check Dongqing's stats.

243
00:12:13,910 --> 00:12:15,120
Let's check Mr. Zhao's as well.

244
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:15,480
Okay.

245
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:21,520
Let's take a look at Yan Yuzhen's again.

246
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,150
Her second skill is Flying Apsaras Dance,

247
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:27,030
with teleportation
and illusory explosions.

248
00:12:27,030 --> 00:12:28,120
Once her energy bar is full,

249
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,440
she can unleash her ultimate move,

250
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:31,200
"Dance of the Rainbow Skirt
and Feathered Robe,"

251
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,000
which also regenerates health.

252
00:12:55,570 --> 00:12:57,700
Her ultimate can even restore health?

253
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,630
Yan Yuzhen's starting HP

254
00:13:01,630 --> 00:13:02,390
is 3,000 points.

255
00:13:02,390 --> 00:13:02,790
Right.

256
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:04,850
Dongqing and Zhao Hengzhi

257
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:05,910
only have

258
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:06,710
1,000 HP each.

259
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,030
Can we do something?

260
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:09,670
I'll see

261
00:13:09,870 --> 00:13:10,840
if I can transmit my voice

262
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:11,600
to Mr. Zhao.

263
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:12,360
Okay.

264
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:13,750
Mr. Zhao?

265
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:22,730
Mr. Zhao,

266
00:13:23,270 --> 00:13:24,320
can you hear me?

267
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,630
We've established a connection

268
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:26,460
with you.

269
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:27,080
Wanping,

270
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:29,510
what do you want to say? Go ahead.

271
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:30,360
Yan Yuzhen's lotus throne

272
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,390
can restore health,

273
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:32,510
and every 10 seconds, it increases

274
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:33,840
her attack power by 10%.

275
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:34,400
Right.

276
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,040
Dongqing,

277
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,640
attack her lotus throne!

278
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:06,470
Dance of the Rainbow Skirt
and Feathered Robe!

279
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:20,910
Which one should we attack?

280
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:22,200
Which one is her real body?

281
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,600
None of them can get away!

282
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:26,850
Samadhi Fire—Heavens Incineration!

283
00:15:03,390 --> 00:15:04,910
Yan Yuzhen, you lose!

284
00:15:05,270 --> 00:15:06,630
Even if you have last words,

285
00:15:06,630 --> 00:15:08,200
I have no interest in hearing them.

286
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,860
I'll finish you off right now.

287
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:41,900
What's happening?

288
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:43,350
A new skill button has

289
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,580
appeared in Yan Yuzhen's skill bar.

290
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:48,240
[Crimson Moon—Goddess Genesis]

291
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,480
When HP drops below 5%,

